# LethalBreed GitIgnore

## Build outputs (regenerable)
.gradle/
build/
run/
out/
.idea/
bin/

## Local documentation (not for GitHub)
structure.md
SKILL.md

## OS files
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db

## Logs
*.log
logs/

## Crash reports
crash-reports/

## Local world data (Fabric run folder sometimes contains this)
*.mca
*.dat
*.lock
